RTRS - WAPET oil partners appoint managing director . West Australian Petroleum Pty Ltd ( WAPET ) , the operator of the Barrow and Thevenard island oilfields off Western Australia , said on Wednesday that Boidy Sibley had been appointed managing director , effective in May . Sibley was currently vice president - exploration and technology for Caltex Pacific Indonesia . He will replace Robert Young who was WAPET managing director for four years and who would become president of the Chevron Petroleum Co in Colombia . WAPET is a joint venture between Texaco Inc , Chevron Inc and Royal Dutch Shell Group , each with two - sevenths stakes , and Mobil Corp with one - seventh . - - Sydney Newsroom 61 - 2 9373 - 1800 
